headline: Aon Announces Quarterly Cash Dividend
summary: Aon plc (NYSE: AON), a leading global professional services firm, today announced that the Board of Directors has declared a quarterly cash dividend of $0.745 per share on Aon's outstanding Class A Ordinary Shares. The dividend is payable February 13, 2026 to shareholders of record on February 2, 2026.

headline: Aon Announces Fourth-Quarter and Full-Year 2025 Earnings Release and Conference Call Date
summary: Aon plc (NYSE: AON), a leading global professional services firm, plans to announce fourth-quarter and full-year 2025 results on Friday, January 30, 2026, in a news release to be issued at 6:30 AM ET.
